messages.content: What does the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node offer for ComfyUI?
The SDXL Resolution Presets custom node provides easy access to the officially supported resolutions in both horizontal and vertical formats.
Which resolutions are available in the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node?
The resolutions available in the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node are 1024x1024, 1152x896, 1216x832, 1344x768, and 1536x640.
Does the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node support landscape and portrait formats?
Yes, the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node supports both horizontal and vertical formats, which includes both landscape and portrait orientations.
How can I utilize the SDXL Resolution Presets in ComfyUI?
To use the SDXL Resolution Presets in ComfyUI, you would navigate to this custom node within the ComfyUI interface and select the desired resolution from the provided options.
